{"tid":1640632,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"田北辰：禁蒙面法或刺激更多年輕人上街","createTime":"2019-10-09T04:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T04:53:59.000Z","uid":24660,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a490a3a492c7274ee4b621d249906e191102773f","tid":1640632,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"田北辰：禁蒙面法或刺激更多年輕人上街<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】立法會議員田北辰指，政府應待社會回復心平氣和才實施禁蒙面法，對現時立法有很大保留，又指現時觸犯禁蒙面法的不少是年輕學生，對緩和示威者情緒只會適得其反。<br />\n田北辰：「十幾歲學生被拘捕會有阻嚇作用，還是刺激更多同學上街，大家要想清楚。成年人知道代價，被捕要坐囚，將來求職難，有其他問題，但對學生而言，同學被警方拘捕，而他們又不是暴力的一群，我所理解很多年輕人認為，因此要出去聲援。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=365609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365609&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ6d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=bb9e88d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365609&h=462662af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=365609</a>"},{"pid":"adfd738dcdce73d6c8ffa24cb4cd0b6103cbb95c","tid":1640632,"uid":182519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:53:59.000Z","msg":"國際文宣組全面進化，大型國際文宣活動&quot;What if they own it&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}